{{Quote|Huttspit! If the designer of these helmets ever had to use them in the field&hellip;|A stormtrooper|<ref name="Isard">''[[X-Wing: Isard's Revenge]]''</ref>}}
"'''Huttspit'''" was a curse in the [[Ciutric Hegemony]].<ref name="Isard" /> It shared similarities with the expression "to give a bucket of Hutt spit (for something)."<ref name="Ruin">''[[The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide II: Ruin]]''</ref>

{{Stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The expletive "Huttspit" was introduced in [[X-Wing: Isard's Revenge|''Isard's Revenge'']], [[Michael A. Stackpole]]'s [[1999]] eight entry in the [[Star Wars: X-Wing (novel series)|''Star Wars: X-Wing'' novel series]].<ref name="Isard" />

